Summary of My Participation – Discussion Post 1

In this discussion, I examined the impact of Industry 4.0 and Industry 5.0 on a sector of interest and explored how advanced technologies, including artificial intelligence, automation, big data, and smart systems, are transforming organisational processes and decision-making. I also analysed a real-world information system failure and discussed its consequences for customers, organisational reputation, operational performance, and financial outcomes. Through this activity, I demonstrated my ability to critically evaluate the opportunities and challenges associated with digital transformation and information systems. The discussion enhanced my understanding of the practical implications of emerging technologies, the importance of reliable information systems, and the role of machine learning and data-driven solutions in modern organisations. Additionally, it strengthened my research, critical thinking, and academic communication skills through the use of relevant academic literature and evidence-based arguments.
